The daily opening times of Questacon in Canberra

The following overview lists the visiting hours for Questacon in Canberra. The hours of the current day (today) are highlighted. Please note that opening hours on special days or holidays may differ from what is displayed here. We therefore recommend you to always check the opening hours with Questacon before your visit and see if it might be needed to reserve a time slot.
